<% layout('layouts/boilerplate')%>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4">About YelpCamp</h1>
    
    <p>YelpCamp is a web application designed to help outdoor enthusiasts discover and share campground experiences across the United States. This platform allows users to:</p>
    
    <ul>
        <li>Browse a diverse collection of campgrounds</li>
        <li>Create and share new campground listings</li>
        <li>Leave reviews and ratings for campgrounds they've visited</li>
        <li>Connect with fellow campers and nature lovers</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4 mb-3">Our Goals</h2>
    
    <p>At YelpCamp, we aim to:</p>
    
    <ol>
        <li>Promote outdoor recreation and appreciation for nature</li>
        <li>Provide a user-friendly platform for campers to share their experiences</li>
        <li>Help campground owners showcase their facilities</li>
        <li>Build a community of camping enthusiasts</li>
        <li>Encourage responsible and sustainable camping practices</li>
    </ol>

    <p class="mt-4">Whether you're a seasoned camper or new to the great outdoors, YelpCamp is here to help you find your next adventure. Join our community today and start exploring!</p>
</div>
